texts.text:
Table, a possible unimplemented block
Crafting table, a block that is used to craft items
Enchantment table, which allows players to enchant tools, armor, and books for the cost of experience
Fletching table, a villager job site block
Cartography table, a table to zoom out, copy and lock maps
Smithing table, a table that can be used to upgrade diamond tools to netherite tools
Lab table, a block used in chemistry for combining different substances in Education Edition
Tutorials/Furniture#Tables, a tutorial on how to build several different structures that simulate real-life tables
Loot table
